snippet.title: Johnny Depp: #MeToo villain or victim? | Ben Davies
snippet.description:
https://bit.ly/2TxhJ5I Ben Davies of The Rebel.Media reports: I’m no fan of actor Johnny Depp, but I believe that everyone is entitled to a presumption of innocence. After his ex-wife Amber Heard accused Depp of being abusive, he was dropped from his blockbuster Pirates of the Caribbean franchise, while Heard was picked up for another. But now Depp is fighting back, suing Heard for $50 million and claiming that her accusations are (wait for it) a hoax. Shades of Jussie Smollett…
